## 8. REDIRECT CARD UI SPECIFICATION

Triggered when FALLBACK JSON is detected in AI response.

Visual design:
  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
  │  ⚠  I couldn't find a reliable answer for this.                │
  │     Here are some resources to help you:                       │
  │                                                                 │
  │  🌐  Google Search          → [Open ↗]                         │
  │  📖  Wikipedia              → [Open ↗]                         │
  │  💻  Stack Overflow         → [Open ↗]  (if coding topic)      │
  │  🎓  Khan Academy           → [Open ↗]  (if learning topic)    │
  │  🔬  arXiv                  → [Open ↗]  (if research topic)    │
  │                                                                 │
  │  [ Search yourself: ________________________________ [Go] ]    │
  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

- Card background: #1a1a1a with amber left border (#f59e0b).
- Each link opens in a new browser tab.
- Query is pre-filled in the search box, editable by user.
- "Go" button opens Google with the edited query.

