## 9. SUCCESS METRICS

| Metric                          | Target                             |
|---------------------------------|------------------------------------|
| Time to first token             | < 1.5 seconds                      |
| Chat load time (cold start)     | < 2 seconds                        |
| Fallback redirect click rate    | > 40% (user finds redirect useful) |
| API key setup completion rate   | > 85%                              |
| Mobile usability score          | ≥ 90 (Lighthouse)                  |
| Accessibility score             | ≥ 90 (Lighthouse)                  |
| Conversation export success     | 100%                               |

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

## 10. OUT OF SCOPE (V1)

- User authentication / accounts (no login required in v1).
- Cloud sync of conversations.
- Team / multi-user collaboration.
- Plugin system.
- Mobile native app (web-only in v1).
- Custom fine-tuned models.
- Billing management (user provides their own key).

