## 11. DEVELOPMENT PHASES

Phase 1 — Core MVP (Weeks 1–3):
  ✓ Project setup (React + Vite + Tailwind + Zustand)
  ✓ API key configuration screen
  ✓ Basic chat UI (send/receive messages)
  ✓ Streaming responses
  ✓ Markdown + code block rendering
  ✓ Conversation history (localStorage)
  ✓ Sidebar with past conversations
  ✓ Fallback detection + redirect card
  ✓ Dark theme (default)

Phase 2 — Polish (Weeks 4–5):
  ✓ Suggested follow-up chips
  ✓ System prompt / persona settings
  ✓ Multiple AI providers support
  ✓ Export conversations
  ✓ Responsive / mobile layout
  ✓ Accessibility improvements
  ✓ Animations & micro-interactions

Phase 3 — Advanced Features (Weeks 6–8):
  ✓ Voice input (Web Speech API)
  ✓ Image / file upload (for vision models)
  ✓ KaTeX math rendering
  ✓ Conversation search
  ✓ Pin and organize chats
  ✓ Custom redirect presets

